<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddb2769ef-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s245"><num value="245">§ 245.</num><heading> Vacancies during recess of Senate</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President shall have power to fill all vacancies that may happen on the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System during the recess of the Senate by granting commissions which shall expire with the next session of the Senate.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddb2769f0-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s10">Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 10</ref> (par.), <ref href="/us/stat/38/260">38 Stat. 260</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1922-06-03/ch205">June 3, 1922, ch. 205</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/42/620">42 Stat. 620</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614">Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614</ref>, title II, § 203(a), 49, Stat. 704.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="iddb2769f1-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="iddb2769f2-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="iddb2769f3-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is comprised of fifth par. of section 10 of act <date date="1913-12-23">Dec. 23, 1913</date>. For classification to this title of other pars. of section 10, see Codification note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t12/s241">section 241 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="iddb2769f4-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I78" topic="changeOfName" id="iddb2769f5-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Change of Name</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 203(a) of act <date date="1935-08-23">Aug. 23, 1935</date>, changed name of Federal Reserve Board to Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
